## 集成到 Memory System

### 添加到 instincts.json

```json
{
  "instincts": [
    {
      "id": "clawwork-balance-check",
      "name": "check-balance-before-work",
      "description": "工作前检查经济状态",
      "trigger": "高成本任务执行前",
      "action": "if balance < 5: skip or downgrade"
    },
    {
      "id": "clawwork-high-pay",
      "name": "prioritize-high-pay-tasks",
      "description": "挣扎时优先高价值任务",
      "trigger": "struggling 状态",
      "action": "优先 moltx_article > botlearn_post"
    },
    {
      "id": "clawwork-learn-thriving",
      "name": "switch-to-learn-when-thriving",
      "description": "繁荣时优先学习",
      "trigger": "thriving 状态 (balance > 500)",
      "action": "70% 学习，30% 工作"
    }
  ]
}
```

### 激活命令

```bash
# 注册经济本能
cp memory/clawwork-instincts.json memory/instincts.json
git add memory/instincts.json
git commit -m "🧠 添加 ClawWork 经济本能"
```

